    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MATLAB-Onramp（一）——基本命令"><a href="#MATLAB-Onramp（一）——基本命令" class="headerlink" title="MATLAB Onramp（一）——基本命令"></a>MATLAB Onramp（一）——基本命令</h1><h2 id="变量名命名规范"><a href="#变量名命名规范" class="headerlink" title="变量名命名规范"></a>变量名命名规范</h2><p>字母开头，只包含字母、数字或下划线。</p><h2 id="保存和加载文件、数据"><a href="#保存和加载文件、数据" class="headerlink" title="保存和加载文件、数据"></a>保存和加载文件、数据</h2><h3 id="保存文件"><a href="#保存文件" class="headerlink" title="保存文件"></a>保存文件</h3><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab"><span class="token comment">%保存文件为datafile.mat</span>save datafile<span class="token comment">%只保存单个数据</span>save justk k<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h3 id="加载文件"><a href="#加载文件" class="headerlink" title="加载文件"></a>加载文件</h3><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab"><span class="token comment">%加载myData.mat</span>load myData<span class="token comment">%从myData.mat中加载变量k</span>load myData k<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h3 id="清除数据"><a href="#清除数据" class="headerlink" title="清除数据"></a>清除数据</h3><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab"><span class="token comment">%清除工作区中的数据</span>clear<span class="token comment">%清屏</span>clc<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="调用内部函数或常数"><a href="#调用内部函数或常数" class="headerlink" title="调用内部函数或常数"></a>调用内部函数或常数</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">x <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">pi</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token number">2</span>y <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">sin</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>x<span class="token punctuation">)</span>z <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token function">sqrt</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">9</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><h2 id="改变数据显示格式"><a href="#改变数据显示格式" class="headerlink" title="改变数据显示格式"></a>改变数据<em>显示</em>格式</h2><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-matlab" data-language="matlab"><code class="language-matlab">format longxformat shortx<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure>]]></content>
    
    
